data.description: Wow, talk about a lot of house and bang for your buck.  This charming and spacious home has a very large living room with a huge and newer dual pane vinyl window that brings the outdoors in. Many windows throughout, all but one small window are newer dual pane vinyl windows, spacious kitchen with skylight. Large step down dining area off the kitchen that can also be used as an office, craft room, or anything else one needs. There is also room in the kitchen for a dinging table. Three bedrooms with an additional room that was converted from the original garage make 4 bedrooms! (2 of the bedrooms have no closets but those could easily be added if needed) & 2 bathrooms, perfect family living, two of the bedrooms have bay windows which adds to the charm of this light, bright, spacious home. Attractive newer laminate flooring, carpet in the bedrooms.  Good size fenced back yard.  Two additional parking spaces to the left of the house, plus street parking,  Very close the the beach! that is a huge bonus and close to the library, schools, and parks  make this location very desirable. This home could be run as a vacation rental as well.  The possibilities are endless.
